n]], southern [[Anhui]], southern [[Hubei]]\n|-\n|  || [[Jiangnandong Circuit (Tang dynasty)|Jiangnandong]]**||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6c5f\u5357\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6c5f\u5357\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ji\u0101ngn\u00e1nd\u014dng}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Suzhou]]||southern [[Jiangsu]], [[Zhejiang]], [[Fujian]], [[Shanghai]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Jingji Circuit (Tang dynasty)|Jingji]]*||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u4eac\u757f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngj\u012b}}||Jingzhao Fu||[[Xi'an]]||[[Xi'an]] and environs\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Lingnan Circuit|Lingnan]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u5dba\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u5cad\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|L\u01d0ngn\u00e1n}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Guangzhou]]||[[Guangdong]], eastern [[Guangxi]], northern [[Vietnam]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Longyou Circuit|Longyou]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u96b4\u53f3}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u9647\u53f3}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|L\u01d2ngyou}}||Shanzhou||[[Ledu County]], [[Qinghai]]||[[Gansu]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Shannan Circuit|Shannan]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u5c71\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Sh\u0101nn\u00e1n}}||  <!-- capital --> ||  ||Shannanxi + Shannandong (see map)\n|-\n|  || [[Shannanxi Circuit|Shannanxi]]**||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u5c71\u5357\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Sh\u0101nn\u00e1nx\u012b}}||Liangzhou||[[Hanzhong]]||southern [[Shanxi]], eastern [[Sichuan]], [[Chongqing]]\n|-\n|  || [[Shannandong Circuit|Shannandong]]**||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u5c71\u5357\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u5c71\u5357\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Sh\u0101nn\u00e1nd\u014dng}}||Xiangzhou||[[Xiangfan]]||southern [[Henan]], [[Hubei]]\n|}\n\n<nowiki>*</nowiki> Circuits established under Xuanzong, as opposed to Taizong's original ten circuits.\n\n<nowiki>**</nowiki> Circuits established under Xuanzong by dividing Taizong's Jiangnan and Shannan circuits.\n\nOther Tang-era circuits include the [[West Lingnan Circuit|West Lingnan]], [[Wu'an Circuit|Wu'an]], and [[Qinhua circuit]]s.\n\n=== Song provinces ===\n[[File:Northern Song Circuits.png|thumb|300px|right|Song circuits, ca. 1111]]\nThe Song government abolished the previous commissioners and renamed their circuits ({{zh|labels=no|c={{linktext|\u8def}} |p=l\u00f9}}, literally meaning \"roads\", but however is still usually translated into English as \"circuits\"). They also added a number of \"army\" prefectures ({{zh|labels=no|t={{linktext|\u8ecd}} |p=j\u016bn}}). Similarly, [[Liao Dynasty|Liao]] and [[Jurchen Jin]] dynasties also established circuits as the first-level administrative division.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"7\" style=\"background: #ffff99;\" | '''Circuits of the Northern Song dynasty'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Name !! rowspan=\"2\"| Traditional<br>Chinese !! rowspan=\"2\"| Simplified<br>Chinese !! rowspan=\"2\"| Pinyin !!colspan=\"2\"| Capital !! rowspan=\"2\"| Approximant extent in terms of modern locations\n|-\n! Ancient name !! Modern location\n|-\n|[[Chengdufu Circuit|Chengdufu]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6210\u90fd\u5e9c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ch\u00e9ngd\u016bf\u01d4}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Chengdu]]||central [[Sichuan]]\n|-\n|[[Fujian Circuit|Fujian]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u798f\u5efa}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|F\u00faji\u00e0n}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Fuzhou]]||[[Fujian]]\n|-\n|[[Guangnan East Circuit|Guangnan East]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u5ee3\u5357\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u5e7f\u5357\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Gu\u01cengn\u00e1nd\u014dng}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Guangzhou]]||eastern [[Guangdong]]\n|-\n|[[Guangnan West Circuit|Guangnan West]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u5ee3\u5357\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u5e7f\u5357\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Gu\u01cengn\u00e1nx\u012b}}||Guizhou||[[Guilin]]||western [[Guangdong]], [[Guangxi]], [[Hainan]]\n|-\n|[[Hebei East Circuit|Hebei East]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6cb3\u5317\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6cb3\u5317\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00e9b\u011bid\u014dng}}||Beijing||[[Daming County]], Hebei||eastern [[Hebei]]\n|-\n|[[Hebei West Circuit|Hebei West]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6cb3\u5317\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00e9b\u011bix\u012b}}||Zhending||[[Zhengding County]], Hebei||western [[Hebei]]\n|-\n|[[Hedong Circuit|Hedong]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6cb3\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6cb3\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00e9d\u014dng}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Taiyuan]]||[[Shanxi]]\n|-\n|[[Huainan East Circuit|Huainan East]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6dee\u5357\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6dee\u5357\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Hu\u00e1in\u00e1nd\u014dng}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Yangzhou]]||central [[Jiangsu]]\n|-\n|[[Huainan West Circuit|Huainan West]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6dee\u5357\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Hu\u00e1in\u00e1nx\u012b}}||Shouzhou||[[Fengtai County]], Anhui||central [[Anhui]]\n|-\n|[[Jiangnan East Circuit (Song dynasty)|Jiangnan East]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6c5f\u5357\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6c5f\u5357\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ji\u0101ngn\u00e1nd\u014dng}}||Jiangning Fu||[[Nanjing]]||southern [[Anhui]]\n|-\n|[[Jiangnan West Circuit (Song dynasty)|Jiangnan West]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6c5f\u5357\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ji\u0101ngn\u00e1nx\u012b}}||Hongzhou||[[Nanchang]]||[[Jiangxi]]\n|-\n|[[Jingdong East Circuit|Jingdong East]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u4eac\u6771\u6771}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u4eac\u4e1c\u4e1c}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngd\u014dngd\u014dng}}||Qingzhou||[[Qingzhou]], Shandong||eastern [[Shandong]]\n|-\n|[[Jingdong West Circuit|Jingdong West]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u4eac\u6771\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u4eac\u4e1c\u897f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngd\u014dngx\u012b}}||Nanjing||south of [[Shangqiu]], Henan||western [[Shandong]]\n|-\n|[[Jinghu North Circuit|Jinghu North]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u834a\u6e56\u5317}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u8346\u6e56\u5317}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngh\u00fab\u011bi}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Jiangling County|Jiangling]]||[[Hubei]], western [[Hunan]]\n|-\n|[[Jinghu South Circuit|Jinghu South]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u834a\u6e56\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u8346\u6e56\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngh\u00fan\u00e1n}}||[[Tanzhou (in modern Hunan)|Tanzhou]]||[[Changsha]]||[[Hunan]]\n|-\n|[[Jingji Circuit (Song dynasty)|Jingji]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u4eac\u757f}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngj\u012b}}||Chenliu||Chenliu, [[Kaifeng]], Henan||[[Kaifeng]] and environs\n|-\n|[[Jingxi North Circuit|Jingxi North]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u4eac\u897f\u5317}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngx\u012bb\u011bi}}||Xijing||[[Luoyang]]||central [[Henan]]\n|-\n|[[Jingxi South Circuit|Jingxi South]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u4eac\u897f\u5357}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|J\u012bngx\u012bn\u00e1n}}||Xiangzhou||[[Xiangfan]]||southern [[Henan]], northern [[Hubei]]\n|-\n|[[Kuizhou Circuit|Kuizhou]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u5914\u5dde}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ku\u00edzh\u014du}}||Kuizhou||[[Fengjie County]], [[Chongqing]]||[[Chongqing]], eastern [[Sichuan]], [[Guizhou]]\n|-\n|[[Liangzhe Circuit|Liangzhe]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u5169\u6d59}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u4e24\u6d59}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Li\u01cengzh\u00e8}}||colspan=\"2\"|[[Hangzhou]]||[[Zhejiang]], southern [[Jiangsu]], [[Shanghai]]\n|-\n|[[Lizhou Circuit|Lizhou]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u5229\u5dde}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|L\u00eczh\u014du}}||Xingyuan||[[Hanzhong]]||northern [[Sichuan]], southern [[Shaanxi]]\n|-\n|[[Qinfeng Circuit|Qinfeng]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u79e6\u9cf3}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u79e6\u51e4}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Q\u00ednf\u00e8ng}}||Qinzhou||[[Tianshui]]||southern [[Gansu]]\n|-\n|[[Yongxingjun Circuit|Yongxingjun]]||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u6c38\u8208\u8ecd}}||{{lang|zh-Hans|\u6c38\u5174\u519b}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Y\u01d2ngx\u012bngj\u016bn}}||Jingzhao||[[Xi'an]]||[[Shaanxi]]\n|-\n|[[Zizhou Circuit|Zizhou]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6893\u5dde}}||{{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Z\u01d0zh\u014du}}||Zizhou||[[Santai County]], Sichuan||central southern [[Sichuan]]\n|}\n\n=== Yuan provinces ===\n[[File:Yuan Provinces.png|thumb|300px|right|Yuan provinces, ca. 1330]]\nChina was reorganised into 11 provinces keeping most of the previous boundaries of provinces created by the previous dynasty unchanged, the [[Yuan Dynasty]] (1271\u20131368) had 2 addition regions: Central region ruled by the [[Zhongshu Sheng]] ({{lang|zh-Hant|\u4e2d\u66f8\u7701}}) and the Tibetan region ruled by the [[Bureau of Buddhist and Tibetan Affairs]] ({{lang|zh-Hans|\u5ba3\u653f\u9662}}).\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"10\" style=\"background: #ffff99;\" | '''Circuits of the Yuan dynasty'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Name !! rowspan=\"2\"| Traditional<br>Chinese !! rowspan=\"2\"| Simplified<br>Chinese !! rowspan=\"2\"| Pinyin !!colspan=\"5\"| Capital !! rowspan=\"2\"| Approximant extent in terms of modern locations\n|-\n! Ancient name || Traditional<br>Chinese || Simplified<br>Chinese || Pinyin || Modern location\n|-\n| [[Gansu]] \n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u7518\u8085}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u7518\u8083}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|G\u0101ns\u00f9}}\n| Ganzhou Circuit\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u7518\u5dde\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u7518\u5dde\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|G\u0101nzh\u014du L\u00f9}}\n| [[Zhangye]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Gansu]], [[Ningxia]], & eastern [[Inner Mongolia]].\n|-\n| [[Huguang Province|Huguang]]\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u6e56\u5ee3}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u6e56\u5e7f}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00fagu\u01ceng}}\n| Wuchang Circuit\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6b66\u660c\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|W\u01d4ch\u0101ng L\u00f9}}\n| [[Wuhan]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Hunan]], [[Guangxi]], [[Guizhou]], [[Hainan]],<br>southern [[Hubei]] & western [[Guangdong]].\n|-\n| [[Henanjiangbei Province|Henanjiangbei]]\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6cb3\u5357\u6c5f\u5317}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00e9n\u00e1nji\u0101ngb\u011bi}}\n| Bianliang Circuit\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6c74\u6881\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Bi\u00e0nli\u00e1ng L\u00f9}}\n| [[Kaifeng]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Henan]], northern [[Hubei]], northern [[Jiangsu]], & northern [[Anhui]].\n|-\n| [[Jiangxi]]\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6c5f\u897f}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ji\u0101ngx\u012b}}\n| Longxing Circuit\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u9f8d\u8208\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u9f99\u5174\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|L\u00f3ngx\u00ecng L\u00f9}}\n| [[Nanchang]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Jiangxi]] & eastern [[Guangdong]].\n|-\n| [[Jiangzhe Province|Jiangzhe]]\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u6c5f\u6d59}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Ji\u0101ngzh\u00e8}}\n| Hangzhou Circuit\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center\"|{{lang|zh|\u676d\u5dde\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|H\u00e1ngzh\u014du L\u00f9}}\n| [[Hangzhou]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Shanghai]], [[Zhejiang]], [[Fujian]], southern [[Jiangsu]], & southern [[Anhui]].\n|-\n| [[Liaoyang Province|Liaoyang]]\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u907c\u967d}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u8fbd\u9633}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Li\u00e1oy\u00e1ng}}\n| Liaoyang Circuit\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u907c\u967d\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u8fbd\u9633\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|Li\u00e1oy\u00e1ng L\u00f9}}\n| [[Liaoyang]]\n| Consist of modern location of [[Heilongjiang]], [[Jilin]], [[Liaoning]], eastern [[Hebei]],<br>northwestern [[Inner Mongolia]], northern [[Korea]], & [[Outer Manchuria]].\n|-\n| [[Lingbei Province|Lingbei]]\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u5dba\u5317}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u5cad\u5317}}\n| {{lang|zh-Latn-pinyin|L\u01d0ngb\u011bi}}\n| Hening Circuit\n| {{lang|zh-Hant|\u548c\u5be7\u8def}}\n| {{lang|zh-Hans|\u548c\